remarks: A singleton cancellation law for dominance.  (Contributed by Stefan O'Rear, 19-Feb-2015.)  (Revised by Stefan O'Rear, 5-May-2015.)
statement:
domunsncan.a $e |- A e. _V $.
domunsncan.b $e |- B e. _V $.
domunsncan $p |- ( ( -. A e. X /\ -. B e. Y ) -> ( ( { A } u. X ) ~<_ ( { B } u. Y ) <-> X ~<_ Y ) ) $.
